{"id": "1377938312685420595", "channel_id": "1377391496617267251", "type": 19, "author_id": "334173481706979329", "author_name": "azurrys", "author_bot": false, "content": "I downloaded the game on Steam and logged in with my account. It functioned normally on my PC, prompting me that I was in the middle of an investigation and asking if I wanted to resume, so I resumed the investigation and continued playing for some time on PC. I finished 1-9 and played for a bit longer (at least finishing 1-10, can't remember if I played longer again before trying the game on my phone) then exited the game on my PC. Some time later I opened it on my phone again. It loaded normally after that! Since I'd finished the investigation, I loaded it up and was just directed to the usual home screen. (To be clear, I didn't make any changes to the game files on my phone at all, the only change was the status that my account was in - which was that I was no longer in the middle of 1-9.)\n\nA few more details on the status: I hadn't progressed far in 1-9 when the loading issue struck, I think I was on the third square or so. I finished 1 battle and that was it.", "timestamp": "2025-05-30T09:14:54.600000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-05-30T09:21:08.052000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1131790839291596841"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1377935562694201395", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1377391496617267251", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Unable to start game - stuck on checking for updates screen", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168893200044183"]}
